{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji15","name":"毛泽东全集第15卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/maoquanji15.pdf"],"article":{"title":"致彭德怀电","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"致彭德怀电!"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1940年11月16日）"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"目前斗争重心应移至淮河流域，蒋介石企图切断八路军与新四军之联系。故提议调三四四旅进至陇海铁路与淮河之间，协助彭雪枫创建抗日根据地，并策应刘少奇处。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1940,"month":11,"day":16}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":230,"page_end":230},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"name":"彭德怀","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}